text: Snake in the Eagle's Shadow () is a 1978 Hong Kong action comedy movie directed by Yuen Woo-ping and starring Jackie Chan, Hwang Jang-lee, Yuen Siu- tien, Dean Shek, Roy Horan. It was distributed by Seasonal Film Corporation. ==Other websites== * * Category:1978 comedy movies Category:1978 action movies Category:Hong Kong comedy movies Category:Hong Kong action movies
